  "title": "Sales Coordinator / Purchaser / Operations Admin (Across SG)",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Hiring for a few roles - B2B Sales Executive / Sales Engineer</p></li><li><p>Industry: Commercial / Catering / F&B / Industrial / Engineering</p></li><li><p>Location: Across Singapore</p></li><li><p>5 days work/week</p></li><li><p>$2500 - $4000 (Basic) - Open to discuss</p></li><li><p>With/without Commission</p></li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Develop and manage B2B customer accounts across assigned industries</p></li><li><p>Identify new business opportunities and follow up on leads</p></li><li><p>Prepare quotations, proposals, and basic costings</p></li><li><p>Liaise with internal teams to ensure smooth order fulfilment</p></li><li><p>Maintain long-term customer relationships and after-sales support</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma / Degree in Business, Engineering, or related field</p></li><li><p>Experience in B2B sales preferred</p></li><li><p>Good communication and negotiation skills</p></li><li><p>Good to have Class 3 Driving License or with own vehicle</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated and target driven</p></li><li></li></ul><p>To Apply, kindly click on the \"APPLY NOW\" button.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>StaffKing Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Chong Kar Ming (John) (R21101412)</p>",
